Title: In search of unknown
DateModified: '2019-02-26'
DatePublished: '2019-02-26'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/in-search-of-unknown
SetInCountry: India
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Akhilesh Bakshi
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "While working in an exciting research assignment protagonist finds interesting\
  \ aspect of his own personality - the search and love for hitherto unknown in his\
  \ life. His first assignment begins in the beautiful hilly landscape of Himachal\
  \ Pradesh (India). Here the protagonist while interacting with his interviewees\
  \ slips into the myriad culture and thoughts of the people who have been living\
  \ there. From daily routines to liesure activities, he starts observing and living\
  \ like the people of hills. His choice of food shifts, his manner of interacting\
  \ with the people changes. Now he is spending more time self reflecting and doing\
  \ activities, which provide him peace and tranquility. \n\nThis story is a journey,\
  \ which begins as an official assignment turns into a personal journey of exploring\
  \ the unexplored depths."
